25:[["$","blockquote",null,{"children":["\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"阅读提示\n适合对象：负责 Web 安全防护和规则治理的开发或安全工程师。\n阅读前提：了解 HTTP、代理、Nginx 或 Apache 基础配置。\n核心收获：掌握 WAF 的部署方式、规则编写与误报调优。\n说明：规则集和模块参数请优先对照当前产品与 OWASP CRS 文档。"}],"\n"]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"Web 应用防火墙（WAF）工作在应用层，专门针对 HTTP/HTTPS 流量进行深度检测和过滤，是防御 SQL 注入、跨站脚本（XSS）、文件上传漏洞等 Web 攻击的关键安全组件。本文将以开源 WAF 引擎 ModSecurity 为核心，讲解其工作原理、部署方法、规则编写和防护策略。"}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"waf-的工作原理","children":["WAF 的工作原理",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#waf-的工作原理","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"WAF 位于 Web 服务器之前（或集成在 Web 服务器中），对每一个 HTTP 请求和响应进行分析。其检测方式主要包括："}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"正则匹配signature-based","children":["正则匹配（Signature-Based）",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#正则匹配signature-based","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":["通过预定义的正则表达式模式匹配请求中的恶意特征，如 SQL 关键字（",["$","code",null,{"children":"UNION SELECT"}],"、",["$","code",null,{"children":"OR 1=1"}],"）、XSS 载荷（",["$","code",null,{"children":"<script>"}],"、",["$","code",null,{"children":"onerror="}],"）等。这是最传统也最常用的检测方式，规则明确、误报可控。"]}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"语义分析semantic-analysis","children":["语义分析（Semantic Analysis）",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#语义分析semantic-analysis","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"超越简单的字符串匹配，理解请求内容的语义。例如，对 SQL 片段进行语法解析，判断是否构成有效的 SQL 注入语句。这种方式能有效应对各类编码和混淆绕过。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"行为分析behavioral-analysis","children":["行为分析（Behavioral Analysis）",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#行为分析behavioral-analysis","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"基于请求频率、访问模式、参数异常等行为特征进行判断。例如同一 IP 短时间内大量请求同一接口，或请求参数长度异常等。通常结合评分机制（Anomaly Scoring）综合判定。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"waf-部署模式","children":["WAF 部署模式",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#waf-部署模式","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",["$","table",null,{"children":[["$","thead",null,{"children":["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","th",null,{"children":"模式"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"说明"}],["$","th",null,{"children":"示例"}]]}]}],["$","tbody",null,{"children":[["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"反向代理"}]}],["$","td",null,{"children":"WAF 作为独立反向代理部署在 Web 服务器前"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"Nginx + ModSecurity"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"嵌入式"}]}],["$","td",null,{"children":"WAF 模块嵌入 Web 服务器"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"Apache mod_security"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"云 WAF"}]}],["$","td",null,{"children":"基于 DNS/CDN 的云端 WAF"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"Cloudflare WAF、AWS WAF"}]]}],["$","tr",null,{"children":[["$","td",null,{"children":["$","strong",null,{"children":"旁路检测"}]}],["$","td",null,{"children":"镜像流量进行分析，不阻断"}],["$","td",null,{"children":"用于监控和审计"}]]}]]}]]}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"modsecurity-部署","children":["ModSecurity 部署",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#modsecurity-部署","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"children":"ModSecurity 是最著名的开源 WAF 引擎，支持 Apache、Nginx 和 IIS。ModSecurity v3（libmodsecurity）采用了与 Web 服务器解耦的架构，通过连接器（Connector）与不同的 Web 服务器集成。"}],"\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"nginx--modsecurity-v3-部署","children":["Nginx + ModSecurity v3 部署",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#nginx--modsecurity-v3-部署","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L2d","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"nginx-配置启用-modsecurity","children":["Nginx 配置启用 ModSecurity",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#nginx-配置启用-modsecurity","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L2e","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"apache--modsecurity-部署","children":["Apache + ModSecurity 部署",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#apache--modsecurity-部署","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L2f","\n",["$","h3",null,{"id":"modsecurity-主配置文件","children":["ModSecurity 主配置文件",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#modsecurity-主配置文件","children":["$","span",null,{"children":"#"}]}]]}],"\n","$L30","\n",["$","h2",null,{"id":"owasp-crs-核心规则集","children":["OWASP CRS 核心规则集",["$","a",null,{"className":"anchor-link","aria-label":"Permalink","href":"#owasp-crs-核心规则集","children":"$L31"}]]}],"\n","$L32","\n","$L33","\n","$L34","\n","$L35","\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","$L36","\n","$L37","\n","$L38","\n","$L39","\n","$L3a","\n","$L3b","\n","$L3c","\n","$L3d","\n","$L3e","\n","$L3f","\n","$L40","\n","$L41","\n","$L42","\n","$L43","\n","$L44","\n","$L45","\n","$L46","\n","$L47","\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","$L48","\n","$L49","\n","$L4a","\n","$L4b","\n","$L4c","\n","$L4d"]
